Ralph Lauren Romance Eau de Parfum - 50 ml (For Women) Price: Rs.3315

A trace of spring a dash of amour - Romance from the acclaimed fashion house of Ralph Lauren is evocative of the eternal sensation of being in love. Delicious beguiling floral and woody accords are artfully infused into this luxury Eau de Parfum by celebrated perfumer Harry Fremont. Joyous and uplifting Romance enshrouds you in its alluring gentle mist.

Dreamy and sensual Romance opens with a delicate top note of rose and trails into a floral spicy heart of white violet sweet water lily lily carnation and fresh ginger. An earthy base note of patchouli oak moss and velvety white musk add a touch of warmth and mystery to the fragrance. Sparkling yet subtle Romance is the fragrance of the free-spirited woman who believes in herself and in all the timeless joys of love.
